{"id":11840,"type":4,"name":"SimCity 4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b1/e2/11840_iU0Iw.jpg","rating":{"total":156,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":3,"6":7,"7":41,"8":61,"9":19,"10":24},"score":8},"summary":"《模擬城市4》（SimCity 4），是一款即時策略及模擬建造城市的電腦遊戲，由美商藝電旗下的Maxis所製作發行，屬於模拟城市系列中的第四集。比起前代，這代加入了更多真實世界都市的要素，而且和前代不同的是，這代可以建造一整個區域內的所有城市，將整個區域給變成一個都會區，並且玩家可以將在模擬市民內的人物輸入遊戲中，讓模擬市民變成都市居民的一份子，藉此更了解整個都市個別區域的發展情況。\r\n本遊戲另有資料片《模拟城市4 尖峰时刻》（SimCity4:Rush hour），大幅擴充了大眾運輸方面的選項。遊戲本體及該資料片之中文版，在台灣等地區係以「模擬城市：福爾摩沙」之名發行。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>模拟城市4</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/32713\">Maxis</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/13930\">Electronic Arts</a></li><li><span>遊戲設計師: </span><a href=\"/person/6286\">Will Wright</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>Win</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Mac OS X</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>SIM</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2003-1-14</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>Maxis</li><li><span>发行公司: </span>EA</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">发行公司: </span>Aspyr Media</li>","collection":{"wish":20,"collect":180,"doing":13,"on_hold":9,"dropped":5},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":32},{"name":"simcity","count":27},{"name":"模拟城市","count":26},{"name":"EA","count":25},{"name":"MAXIS","count":16},{"name":"SIM","count":10},{"name":"模拟系列","count":9},{"name":"2003","count":6},{"name":"童年","count":5},{"name":"模拟建设","count":4},{"name":"费时间","count":4},{"name":"mod","count":4},{"name":"20-25","count":2},{"name":"模拟经营","count":2},{"name":"非常好玩","count":1},{"name":"城市","count":1},{"name":"模拟","count":1},{"name":"STEAM","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":32713,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/73/32713_prsn_v6T1g.jpg","name":"Maxis","desc":"开发"},{"id":13930,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ed/80/13930_prsn_10ahO.jpg","name":"艺电","desc":"发行"},{"id":6286,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/71/5b/6286_prsn_y3MY8.jpg","name":"威尔·莱特","desc":"遊戲設計師"}],"relations":[{"id":14408,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/79/bb